Description: Essential oils and resinoids; perfumery, cosmetic or toilet preparations

Subentries.Description: Pre-shave, shaving or after-shave preparations, personal deodorants, bath preparations, depilatories and other perfumery, cosmetic or toilet preparations, not elsewhere specified or included; prepared room deodorizers, whether or not perfumed or having disinfectant properties:
Preparations for perfuming or deodorizing rooms, including odoriferous preparations used during religious rites:
"Agarbatti" and other odoriferous preparations which operate by burning
